title: Funnydruids

content: [H] PayPal [W] BTC - $220I prefer to send to a Swedish PayPal account. Start with a low amount.I will go first, so newbies or risky accounts, you dont need to reply.Only old school good reputation accounts.

comments.body: Quote from: Funnydruids on October 16, 2022, 12:57:02 PM[H] PayPal [W] BTC - $220I prefer to send to a Swedish PayPal account. Start with a low amount.I will go first, so newbies or risky accounts, you dont need to reply.Only old school good reputation accounts.Sorry to be the one that breaks it to you, but those who have old-school good-reputation accounts know that accepting PayPal from a newbie is extremely risky.  Going first won't make any difference.  I doubt you're going to get anyone to take your offer.
